---
title: Double Creamy Tex-Mex Pulled Pork Fusilli with Cheddar & Coriander
description: Here’s a cuisine combo we’re excited to try - Mexican and Italian! Pulled pork is cooked in a creamy tomato sauce with Tex-Mex spices, before being tossed through golden twirls of fusili and Cheddar cheese. This meal is sure to be a hit with the whole family!
